title: Faith Of The Foe (Fandom House - 1987) (Rumor-Novus-HD)
description:
Story by Matt Howarth and W. E. Rittenhouse. Art and cover by Matt Howarth. Part three of The Fire Shrine Trilogy (after This Is Heat), set in the world of Howarths characters Savage Henry and the Post Brothers. While the Posts try to rescue Caroline from the Cubists, Hiroshima launches her final attack. 56 pages, B&W. Mature readers.
